name: IN10S (sztrovacsek)
description:
IN10S (‘intense’) is a classic 2D deathmatch, but every 10 seconds you swap characters with each other. You can see your health and amount of ammo above your character. You can refill the ammo by collecting crates.

Player 01
WASD - Move
Space - Shoot

Player 02
Arrow Keys - Move
Enter - Shoot

Press F to toggle fullscreen.

Credits
Assets by Kenney
Music by Donát Baracsi 
Game by sztrovacsek
